replies.body:
If you're connecting from outside of Korea, there could be routing issues along the way. Keep in mind that the Korean server is meant to serve players only in Korea, so routing issues to that server from outside of the immediate region may be common. The first step, though, is to ensure your local network settings are compatible with our [network guide.
](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues)

Let me know if you have any questions.
